messages.messageBody:
we live about 300 miles away and have a daughter that lives in Denver,
the Denver Zoo and the Denver Mint are wonderful, I am not sure if you
still have to call and make an appointment at the mint, but they will
give you a tour and show you how money is minted, it is very interesting.
There is also several museums, but I am not sure of the names.
Sharon

messages.msgSnippet: Does anyone live in or near Denver and have recommendations for kids activities in or near the city? We are planning on accompanying my husband next week on
messages.messageBody:
Does anyone live in or near Denver and have recommendations for kids'
activities in or near the city? We are planning on accompanying my husband
next week on his business trip to Denver; we will driving there (ie:
cross-country geography field trip!), and will be in Denver for a week. I
would appreciate any helpful tips from anyone who has visited there or
knows the area.

Thanks!
Olivia
